,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:12:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得呢啲情況車上面啲人完全冇錯喎 .... 點解個返法例會搞到咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該要改例</blockquote><br />\n今次判罪明顯因為睇手機而唔係撞到人本身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係點解學神要罰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680c59e79bd4d0929d23e68568619094c4ed6dfa","tid":108191,"uid":430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:14:20.000Z","msg":"學神得學習駕駛牌被判不小心駕駛？<br />\n牌都冇，會唔會扣5分？"},{"pid":"1c2341bf4a065cf8a4cc5539406dd3736f78b4de","tid":108191,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:15:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>半米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點停得切，80%事主<br />\n15%師傅，5%學神</blockquote><br />\n唔係事主就係師傅"},{"pid":"ab8fccb8c95917e139a6df69f1b40f15304cc815","tid":108191,"uid":6495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:17:27.000Z","msg":"學神好撚慘<br />\n雖然今鋪唔關佢事 <br />\n但成世有陰影"},{"pid":"1defe211162eb4394f781b3dd7f159f8a288485c","tid":108191,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我覺得呢啲情況車上面啲人完全冇錯喎 .... 點解個返法例會搞到咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該要改例</blockquote><br />\n今次判罪明顯因為睇手機而唔係撞到人本身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係點解學神要罰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學神認罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />律師證明唔到突然衝出掛<br />\n<br />\n駕駛者在駕車時必須小心注意其他的道路使用者（特別是行人），大概已毋須多言。《道路使用者守則》亦明確表示：「無論何時何地，即使行人胡亂橫過馬路，駕駛人在法律上和道義上，均有責任，提防和避免撞倒行人。因此，你應該經常讓路給行車道上的行人。」法庭亦曾多次強調，車輛由不負責任的駕駛者駕駛，可以成為非常致命的武器。因此，駕駛者應時刻保持警覺，以免危害甚至殺害無辜的市民。雖說行人可能突然衝出馬路以致被車撞倒，但法庭需看到充分證據，證明所謂的「突然衝出」，才可令駕駛者脫罪。"},{"pid":"c72a63f85c3e2dc3efaf0dc9f0600caf63f48702","tid":108191,"uid":13274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:19:01.000Z","msg":"淨係反應距離都已經半米幾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未計stopping distance"},{"pid":"e7fdeffbc92bc127145b043d7e1b3ee7fab76b72","tid":108191,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:21:23.000Z","msg":"假設反應時間係0.2秒, 架車有神brake一踩即刻減速到0, 即係行車速度要低過9km/hr先唔會撞到佢, 香港法律真係好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df58dc2c40290841098c37efbef57b8dcfb4c13","tid":108191,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:22:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三個人都有錯</blockquote><br />\n3個人？<br />\n其中一個變左只鬼了👻"},{"pid":"dfb15b56381c54b98f1987f90847b839a30aaab3","tid":108191,"uid":59746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:23:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得呢啲情況車上面啲人完全冇錯喎 .... 點解個返法例會搞到咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該要改例</blockquote><br />\n咁死左人<br />\n點都要交代下<br />\n所以咪判服務令<br />\n<br />\n不過廢老自己死算啦<br />\n累到車主有心理陰影同案底呢下先慘"},{"pid":"7ef2cd36b7cf1d8f9dddd3b647399a56c5ca58de","tid":108191,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:25:11.000Z","msg":"個教車個個廢老肯定無裝車cam啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9d0c259f667bf39b64e2f1f33fa005e38b8649","tid":108191,"uid":18187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:25:58.000Z","msg":"時速15-20都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class