ssets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以咪告不小心駕駛 唔係告危險駕駛引致他人死亡囉<br />\n<br />\n如果師傅/學神踩咗但踩唔切》 無責任。<br />\n但唔踩就甩唔哂"},{"pid":"8106ca86302b2a0c2336a19fefa919a93d01901b","tid":108191,"uid":59746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T09:51:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>時速15-20都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 輾過去？</blockquote><br />\n我都諗緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只要唔係輾，其實都好難撞得死</blockquote><br />\n60歲<br />\n可能撞到頭，急性中風死<br />\n真係審死官果句<br />\n今日打左你一野，十年後佢香左又關我事咩..."},{"pid":"77e90731842c51f252ee727ecf9cdaa1dfb28aa9","tid":108191,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T09:59:13.000Z","msg":"半米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />車神都停唔切啦下話，呢啲人死都要累埋人"},{"pid":"c8463814cafab43118bf394b5118770d6f68fe59","tid":108191,"uid":837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一句講曬,總之而家個法例就係根本k型嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n路人根本無敵</blockquote><br />\n法例對司機嚴都合理既。 個師傅無分神應該剎得切</blockquote><br />\nOn 9 點撚剎得切 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983ab2f5375c25de31a3d4354da10231a613ed68","tid":108191,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:16:28.000Z","msg":"根本過馬路都應該要考牌 下下係啲死車側邊閃出黎又唔睇路 預知都剎唔切啦"},{"pid":"cfe97dcff87028f24733ea7323ad153c7218c10b","tid":108191,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:16:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該判師父坐監啦<br />\n屌佢有break踩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n師父應該永久停牌</blockquote><br />\n收返佢個牌啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" clas