lass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺明係途人on9<br />\n個官都係做樣罰下"},{"pid":"82ee15731a520e7dd871cb7f828cb142b3ab7e5e","tid":108191,"uid":23221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:17:41.000Z","msg":"如果半米dup得切， 果個唔係人而係神。"},{"pid":"840fab4e649a5fe5d75196bedeb9aa8ebf85b196","tid":108191,"uid":37760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:22:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f3c7fc474c14ad8aafb30d4a2c4cc21d57675f5","tid":108191,"uid":59746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:28:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傻既 只係講有人衝出黎，收唔切咪得，係要同差佬講埋自己點唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺明係途人on9<br />\n個官都係做樣罰下</blockquote><br />\n有案底<br />\n累撚死人"},{"pid":"d12e3e84c722029f174c67898b5c1f0b70f3f189","tid":108191,"uid":28054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:34:58.000Z","msg":"半米係師傅同學神講姐, 又冇車cam <br />\n咁聽落咪唔關佢地事囉, 師傅肯定負最大責任"},{"pid":"6b4f2ce4d69597ca4cb1012e936c5ffa6992f0bc","tid":108191,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:47:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n路人根本無敵</blockquote><br />\n法例對司機嚴都合理既。 個師傅無分神應該剎得切</blockquote><br />\nOn 9 點撚剎得切 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大剎應該開追悼會。一定剎得切。15-20烤<br />\n利申：揸hiace搵食"},{"pid":"a63b125a7d1931e2147b51bfc7c535590fd03983","tid":108191,"uid":5725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:48:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>半米係師傅同學神講姐, 又冇車cam <br />\n咁聽落咪唔關佢地事囉, 師傅肯定負最大責任</blockquote><br />\n雖然OLD NEWS.<br />\n 但有古怪啦, 屌你撞死人,  你冇CAM冇盛.<br />\n如果真係半米距離我覺得就算係師傅直接講反應唔黎都講得去.<br />\n但佢竟然要講佢自己咁岩睇電話所以睇唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb907cac83e2e94bb1901356bae480c06961ded9","tid":108191,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:55:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9dee67df204a87d39adebd92acd8c3912dfe9a7e","tid":108191,"uid":59746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:56:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>半米係師傅同學神講姐, 又冇車cam <br />\n咁聽落咪唔關佢地事囉, 師傅肯定負最大責任</blockquote><br />\n雖然OLD NEWS.<br />\n 但有古怪啦, 屌你撞死人,  你冇CAM冇盛.<br />\n如果真係半米距離我覺得就算係師傅直接講反應唔黎都講得去.<br />\n但佢竟然要講佢自己咁岩睇電話所以睇唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點奇怪法<br />\n年中唔少人因為嫌麻煩所以直接認罪<br />\n<br />\ncharge 條罪都只係不小心駕駛，唔係危險駕駛<br />\n撞死人重要花廳都唔使坐<br />\n算判得好輕"},{"pid":"91c8ada3555f546ee8e59a1097cb11f934f5a341","tid":108191,"uid":17198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>半米喎屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你跨一個大步都唔只半米啦<br />\n點煞，仲要人衝出黎頭行先<br />\n客貨車車身高撞到都正常<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁撚樣俾佢累一獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁話"},{"pid":"39b374aae7f63702681ad992d6cd634a7b8d3aad","tid":108191,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:02:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當時車速15-20km/hr<br />\n攞中間當佢17.5km/hr<br />\n換算返姐係4.861m/s<br />\n半米距離既反應時間姐係0.5/4.861=0.1028s<br />\n一般人由眼睛見到到作出反應大約要0.5s<br />\n我係官既話會判師父同學神無罪<br />\n兼且要賠償佢地既心靈創傷<br />\n等班廢老唔敢再趕住去死咁亂衝出馬路</blockquote><br />\n但師傅都有責任<br />\n學神唔太可以完全路面情況<br />\n你計反應時間無計到個廢伯踏步出馬路既時間<br />\n有break 唔代表唔會撞但未必咁傷"},{"pid":"7503f05ba2a9801fd8701b5e4d077fe3d0702807","tid":108191,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:20:57.000Z","msg":"半米呀<br />\n跟本條撚樣係抵撚死架<br />\n最好送呢啲陷家剷落車底參觀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b58944632e8254ca87b54aed5765ce0ca5f9e5","tid":108191,"uid":54066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所謂半米係佢地一面之詞</blockquote><br />\n呢d無得吹架， 睇距離同傷勢太約有數得計"},{"pid":"840b45032caa56f6638ba5c89f6a224177326c15","tid":108191,"uid":28054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T00:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>所謂半米係佢地一面之詞</blockquote><br />\n呢d無得吹架， 睇距離同傷勢太約有數得計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係咁法官又會話冇證據得半米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8e261607534252ff7339588f79de570756f3a1","tid":108191,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T00:57:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>所謂半米係佢地一面之詞</blockquote><br />\n呢d無得吹架， 睇距離同傷勢太約有數得計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係咁法官又會話冇證據得半米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇剎車痕，貨車同死者倒地距離<br />\n應該計得到"},{"pid":"e001303ecb1dfc2654e937ee9a6e3909a3074a9b","tid":108191,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T01:00:41.000Z","msg":"應該就差佬落口供時tum佢地認罪<br />\n差佬好鍾意咁，話認罪最好,<br />\n唔識法律又一支公俾人困住48小時，<br />\n好易俾差佬影響<br />\n<br />\nBtw想知個後生仔要唔要留案底<br />\n如果要，就真係好無辜"},{"pid":"47df63b8d866d2e3cc22ace1744fc281e1ded344","tid":108191,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T01:12:35.000Z","msg":"抵啦, 衝出馬路抵撚死"},{"pid":"3f65221ef82cc74ce4bd0646d6ad0d019c6ca251","tid":108191,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T01:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>傻既 只係講有人衝出黎，收唔切咪得，係要同差佬講埋自己點唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺明係途人on9<br />\n個官都係做樣罰下</blockquote><br />\n有案底<br />\n累撚死人</blockquote><br />\n社會服務令係有案底架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10104035792a3f27a8ff3aa3010e9c61e1afc6aa","tid":108191,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T01:15:14.000Z","msg":"當年我學車個師傅全程訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩我手車掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8762f377f5661360804b35d80892cc2f3d7851c1","tid